      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained by its previous owner. The engine starts up without hesitation and the transmission provides smooth shifting, making it an excellent candidate for a dependable daily driver. While the interior is clean and well-kept, the exterior shows some light surface scratches and minor paint chips consistent with its age. All major systems are functioning properly, and it has recently undergone a routine inspection to ensure its roadworthiness. Prospective buyers can expect a solid, honest car that is ready for many more miles.",
