      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. The coachwork remains devoid of imperfections, while the cabin retains its factory-fresh integrity and olfactory profile. This vehicle has undergone a rigorous diagnostic evaluation to confirm its mechanical superiority, ensuring it meets the requirements of the most sophisticated automotive enthusiast. This represents a rare opportunity to acquire a definitive example of the model in peerless condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
